OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FA father has praised medical staff who
OL,8,Fcared for his teenage son as he
OL,9,Funderwent surgery for a brain tumour
OL,10,Fusing innovative technology.
OL,12,FThe 3D exoscope, which is designed to
OL,13,Fenhance precision during complex brain
OL,14,Fsurgery and improve outcomes, has been
OL,15,Fintroduced at the Royal Hospital for
OL,16,FChildren in Glasgow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FNHS Greater Glasgow and Clyde said it
OL,8,Fhas become the first in Scotland to
OL,9,Finstall the B Braun Aesculap Aeos 3D
OL,10,FRobotic Assisted Exoscope, which
OL,11,Fprovides "exceptional" image quality,
OL,12,Fpowerful illumination and enhanced
OL,13,Fdepth perception.
OL,15,FToby Peart, 13, from Strathpeffer in
OL,16,Fthe Highlands, was one of the first
OL,17,Fpatients to undergo surgery using the
OL,18,Fsystem.
OL,26,@sD@JOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FHe began experiencing pins and needles
OL,8,Fand pain in his left leg in April 2025
OL,9,Fand his symptoms became progressively
OL,10,Fworse over the course of several
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,FHe had an MRI scan at Raigmore
OL,14,FHospital in Inverness which found he
OL,15,Fhad a brain tumour, and within days he
OL,16,Fwas referred to the Glasgow facility
OL,17,Ffor specialist treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FAn operation was recommended after
OL,8,Ffurther investigations confirmed a
OL,9,Ftumour measuring about 13`14mm on the
OL,10,Fright side of his brain, which proved
OL,11,Fto be non-cancerous, and he underwent
OL,12,Fsurgery in November 2025.
OL,14,FHis father Marc said: "It was without
OL,15,Fquestion the hardest few weeks of our
OL,16,Flives. Toby is a quiet, gentle boy who
OL,17,Fnever complains, so when he told us he
OL,18,Fwas in pain, we knew something wasn't
OL,19,Fright.
OL,26,@vD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,F"Everything happened incredibly
OL,8,Fquickly. One day we were expecting to
OL,9,Fwait a couple of weeks for MRI results
OL,10,Fand the next we were being told that
OL,11,FToby had a brain tumour and needed
OL,12,Fspecialist treatment in Glasgow. It
OL,13,Fwas a huge shock for all of us."
OL,15,FHe and his wife Adie were advised by
OL,16,Fthe surgical teams that post-surgery
OL,17,Foutcomes could include loss of sight
OL,18,For paralysis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FWhen Toby woke from surgery, he
OL,8,Finitially experienced weakness and
OL,9,Fparalysis on his left side, but he
OL,10,Fwent on to make rapid progress during
OL,11,Fhis recovery with support from a
OL,12,Fmultidisciplinary team.
OL,14,FMr Peart said: "When Toby came out of
OL,15,Fsurgery, he couldn't move his left arm
OL,16,For leg and couldn't feel anything. At
OL,17,Fthat point, we didn't know whether
OL,18,Fthat would be permanent or whether
OL,19,Fthings would improve.
OL,26,@vD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,F"A few days later, I woke up and saw
OL,8,Fhim using his right hand to lift his
OL,9,Fleft hand into the air. He looked at
OL,10,Fme and said, 'Dad, quick, look, my
OL,11,Ffingers are doing finger things.' It
OL,12,Fwas one of the most remarkable moments
OL,13,Fof my life.
OL,15,F"Every day he got a little stronger.
OL,16,FThe care he received was incredible
OL,17,Fand it was amazing to watch his
OL,18,Fdetermination.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,F"Just a week after surgery, we were
OL,8,Ftold he was ready to go home. Walking
OL,9,Fout of the hospital with Toby was an
OL,10,Femotional moment and one we'll never
OL,11,Fforget. We're so grateful to
OL,12,F(neurosurgeon) Mr O'Kane and the
OL,13,Fentire team who cared for him.
OL,15,F"We know not every family's journey is
OL,16,Fthe same, but we feel incredibly
OL,17,Ffortunate. Toby was back at school in
OL,18,FJanuary and he's doing really well."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FThe technology has also been designed
OL,8,Fwith the wellbeing of surgeons in mind
OL,9,Fand enables them to work in a more
OL,10,Fupright posture as it features a
OL,11,F"heads-up" 3D display, unlike
OL,12,Ftraditional microscopes that require
OL,13,Fprolonged "head-down" positioning.
OL,15,FRoddy O'Kane, consultant neurosurgeon
OL,16,Fat NHS Greater Glasgow and Clyde,
OL,17,Fsaid: "Traditionally, neurosurgery
OL,18,Fmeant working for hours with your eyes
OL,19,Ffixed to microscope eyepieces.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@JO]uD@KOUuD@UO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,F"This technology allows us to operate
OL,8,Fupright while gaining views and angles
OL,9,Fthat simply aren't possible with
OL,10,Fconventional microscopes.
OL,12,F"For children undergoing brain
OL,13,Fsurgery, that enhanced visualisation
OL,14,Fcan make a real difference.
OL,16,F"The ability to see more clearly and
OL,17,Freach more effectively supports safer
OL,18,Fsurgery and, ultimately, better
OL,19,Foutcomes."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784546294
OL,3,CBoy, 13, 'doing really well' after
OL,4,Cbrain tumour operated on with new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FEmer Campbell, clinical lead and
OL,8,Fconsultant neurosurgeon at the health
OL,9,Fboard, said: "We're delighted to have
OL,10,Fthis technology in place.
OL,12,F"Beyond the clear benefits for our
OL,13,Fpatients, we're already seeing how it
OL,14,Fenhances teamwork, workflow and
OL,15,Ftraining in theatre."
OL,26,@qD@NOUtD@AOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
